metadata.name: We choose violence #1/13
metadata.description: We follow a "Bunnies Gang" who love nothing more than having fun by breaking the rules and engaging in violent activities. Despite their penchant for chaos, however, these gang have a deep bond and a fierce loyalty to one another. As they navigate the seedy underbelly of their city, they find themselves in all kinds of dangerous situations - but they always come out on top thanks to their sheer strength and fearless attitudes.
